Feeling a Little Bit down about the Elections?Â  Show them that they did not damper our enthusiasm but strengthened our resolve! Join us tomorrow for: "A Great Day for Freedom!"

Great News Everyone! Rhode Island Oath Keepers has been officially invited to march in the Wakefield the Veterans Day Parade. We will be mustering on Oak Street in Wakefield at 12 o'clock noon, please consider joining us to show support for our veterans and bring your friends. Refreshments following!
